high_descs: Head left to the wall, turn left, hang a left at the microwave and walk to the island counter to the left.
Pick up the white mug to the right of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Put the mug inside the fridge on the top shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, walk forward and turn around to face the cabinets next to the fridge.
Open the lower left cabinet, put the chilled mug inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the left and the left again. Turn left and face the island on the left.
Pick up the cup from the left side of the counter.
Turn around and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door and then open it. Take the cup out and shut the door.
Carry the cup and take a step backward.
Open the bottom cabinet and place the cup inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the microwave, hang a  left and walk towards the door, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the white mug off of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk up to the fridge.
Put the white mug in the upper compartment of the fridge and close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the mug, then close the door.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and take two steps and turn around.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the counter to the right of the fridge and put the chilled mug inside then close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in a cabinet.
